theorem closure_interior_union_eq_closure_union_of_P2
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hA : Topology.P2 (X := X) A) (hB : Topology.P2 (X := X) B) :
    closure (interior (A : Set X)) ∪ closure (interior B) =
      closure (A ∪ B : Set X) := by
  -- Rewrite `closure A` and `closure B` using `P2`.
  have hA_eq : closure (A : Set X) = closure (interior A) :=
    (Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_of_P2 (X := X) (A := A) hA).symm
  have hB_eq : closure (B : Set X) = closure (interior B) :=
    (Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_of_P2 (X := X) (A := B) hB).symm
  -- Use the equality `closure (A ∪ B) = closure A ∪ closure B`.
  calc
    closure (interior (A : Set X)) ∪ closure (interior B)
        = closure (A : Set X) ∪ closure B := by
          simpa [hA_eq, hB_eq]
    _ = closure (A ∪ B : Set X) := by
          simpa using (closure_union (A : Set X) B).symm

theorem closure_interior_eq_closure_of_P2 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : Topology.P2 (X := X) A) :
    closure (interior A) = closure (A : Set X) := by
  simpa using
    (Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_of_P2 (X := X) (A := A) hA).symm
